# NolTurn Development Rules

This project belongs to NolTurn Solutions.

## Stack

- Node.js
- Next.js
- TypeScript
- Supabase
- Vercel

## Forbidden unless explicitly requested

- Quickbase
- DCS
- employer systems
- unrelated platforms

## Required behavior

Before coding:
- create an implementation plan
- list affected files
- list assumptions
- identify database impact
- identify security risks

During coding:
- make minimal file changes
- avoid unrelated refactors
- avoid unnecessary dependencies
- preserve existing behavior
- keep code readable

For Supabase:
- never expose service role keys in client code
- consider RLS on every table change
- validate user input before writes
- document migrations clearly

Before finishing:
- review the diff
- identify risks
- provide test steps
- provide rollback notes
